{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 46779, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "Septyryx", "body": "You don't need a key to zone in to this instance, just a raid group.\nIt's located on the south side of Hellfire Citadel down at the bottom ground level. There is a summoning stone down there. \n\nTrash is on a one hour cooldown from the first death. There are four packs of 3 mobs. One of them roams. \nKilling him finishes Trial of the Naaru: Magtheridon ( http://www.wowhead.com/?quest=10888 )", "date": "2007-03-05T21:39:44-06:00", "rating": 68, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "on a sidenote, make sure you kill all the thrash before you engage Magtheridon, else you will have to handle a little more than just the 5 Hellfire Channelers", "creationdate": "2007-03-26T16:21:27-05:00", "id": 4663, "rating": 45, "commentid": 46779, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Vesper", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Easy soloed the boss by feral druid tank (dps gear,tank talents) in patch 4.2.", "creationdate": "2011-08-27T12:09:56-05:00", "id": 490679, "rating": -3, "commentid": 46779, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bnecse", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 53319, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "SilverKnight", "body": "As well as Magtheridon, there are 5 Hellfire Channelers in his room that summon fire adds. The toughest part of the fight is trying to survive taking the Channelers down whilst keeping their summoned adds and Magtheridon under control. It's easy to get overwhelmed. As the Channelers go down, you need to move healers on to the other tanks, because they get stronger and faster with fewer of them up.", "date": "2007-03-18T18:14:49-05:00", "rating": 47, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Warlocks should focus on nothing but making sure you have your infernals banished and feared. 3 warlocks at least is a MUST in this fight and they must be spread out around the room making sure they cover all possible infernal spawn locations.", "creationdate": "2007-05-01T17:45:25-05:00", "id": 295893, "rating": 0, "commentid": 53319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "47989", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I watched a Level 95 Paladin take them all on and win. I was stuck outside the gate. Be sure everyone enters room before starting this fight!!", "creationdate": "2012-03-19T17:19:18-05:00", "id": 528468, "rating": -16, "commentid": 53319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Pypode", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "I think he ment 85.", "creationdate": "2012-12-27T15:00:03-06:00", "id": 616352, "rating": 3, "commentid": 53319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "RiftWalker", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "responseroles": "2056", "responseuser": "adashiel", "response": "", "lastEdit": ["2011-09-22T15:28:11-05:00", 1, "adashiel"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 78560, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "49153", "body": "Actually Illidan kills Magtheridon in Warcraft 3 Expansion Blood Elf campain. How comes he lives in WoW?", "date": "2007-05-06T08:47:18-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "\"Recently it was discovered that after his defeat, Magtheridon was dragged all the way to Hellfire Peninsula and is locked up in a lair created for him underneath Hellfire Citadel, his blood being used to create fel orcs for Illidan Stormrage.\" -via Wowpedia.com", "creationdate": "2011-12-25T02:52:12-06:00", "id": 501079, "rating": 0, "commentid": 78560, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "388145", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
