{"commentv2": 1, "number": 20, "id": 260990, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "91384", "body": "Just FYI to confirm, we killed Mag last night on the live realm, all the changes are accurate.  He's is 110% easier (not that he was hard to begin with): only one infernal per channeler, ceiling fall damage reduced, click debuff reduced, etc.\n\nAlso, he dropped:\n\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=34845][Pit Lord's Satchel][/url]x1\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=34846][Black Sack of Gems][/url]x1\n----- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=32227][Crimson Spinel][/url]\n----- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=32228][Empyrean Sapphire][/url]\n----- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=32229][Lionseye][/url]\n----- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=23436][Living Ruby][/url]\n----- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=23438][Star of Elune][/url]\n----- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=23440][Dawnstone][/url]\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29754][Chestguard of the Fallen Champion][/url]x2\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29755][Chestguard of the Fallen Hero][/url]x1\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29458][Aegis of the Vindicator][/url]x1\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=28774][Glaive of the Pit][/url]x1\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=32385][Magtheridon's Head][/url]x1\n- [url=http://www.wowhead.com/?item=29434][Badge of Justice][/url]x3\n\n... and 250 gold ...\n\nYay loot pinata!", "date": "2008-03-27T09:19:31-05:00", "rating": 26, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "We got about the same, but 510 gold not 250...", "creationdate": "2008-03-29T11:12:31-05:00", "id": 29558, "rating": 8, "commentid": 260990, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zeelian", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Since the Shattering, players have grown powerful enough to solo the smaller TBC raids, so Blizz cut down the cash drops. Mags and Gruul pay 25g each, and Karazhan bosses drop about 4g each. As of 4.3, bosses in Sepentshrine Cavern and the Black Temple still give 250 gold each.", "creationdate": "2012-01-16T14:24:58-06:00", "id": 508806, "rating": 0, "commentid": 260990, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "FurySpec", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Black temple bosses are only giving 10g each in 5.4. Today from mag I got 19.43 gold, 3 epic gems (15g total), 2 rare gems (6g total), 3 class tokens (15g total), a 20g offhand item and a 4g belt. Total vendor value: 80g for a 5 minute instance", "creationdate": "2014-04-14T14:56:21-05:00", "id": 740491, "rating": 0, "commentid": 260990, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "gen3ric", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-03-27T09:20:23-05:00", 1, "91384"]}
