{"commentv2": 1, "number": 31, "id": 572611, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "90072", "body": "3 Manned\r\n\r\nHoly Paladin\r\nUnholy DK\r\nFrost DK (Tank)\r\n\r\nTank tanks everything while the Unholy DK graps them 1 by 1 and finish the adds off away from the others while the healer stands between the Tank and the other DK to keep them up.\r\n\r\nChallenging fight :-)\r\n\r\nhttp://vimeo.com/2896596", "date": "2009-01-21T06:48:07-06:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Recently five-manned, but we couldn't kill the channelers; we just tanked them while we killed magtheridon, and they despawned as soon as we exited his chamber.  You'll have to do this if you don't have an off tank since all five channelers heal the one channeler at low health.", "creationdate": "2009-02-15T21:47:56-06:00", "id": 388712, "rating": 1, "commentid": 572611, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "60495", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just 3 manned with a feral druid, ret pally, and holy priest. I was the holy priest, and I gotta say that without prayer of mending I would not have been able to do this. We left the channelers up and just tanked them throughout the fight.", "creationdate": "2009-03-16T01:35:36-05:00", "id": 394235, "rating": 1, "commentid": 572611, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "32144", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "[quote]3 Manned  Holy Paladin Unholy DK Frost DK (Tank)  Tank tanks everything while the Unholy DK graps them 1 by 1 and finish the adds off away from the others while the healer stands between the Tank and the other DK to keep them up.  Challenging fight :-)  http://vimeo.com/2896596[/quote]  Not sure why this got voted down? The post wasn't arrogant or elitist? It was actually a pretty cool video to watch...  some one jealous maybe?", "creationdate": "2009-03-21T10:35:18-05:00", "id": 86720, "rating": 35, "commentid": 572611, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "200192", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
