{"commentv2": 1, "number": 33, "id": 738332, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "236163", "body": "Magtheridon was voiced by [url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Earl_Boen]Earl Boen[/url], who also donated his voice to narrate in Burning Crusade and Wrath of the Lich King.\r\n\r\nIt appears that he also voiced King Terenas the 2nd in the [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K7k9fUqbcyE]Wrath of the Lich King Cinematic[/url]", "date": "2009-06-05T19:53:27-05:00", "rating": 17, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 34, "id": 739061, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "swbang86", "body": "just 3 manned him. dropped about ~500 gold, so we each earned about 165~ish gold, 3 t4 tokens, a 20 slot bag, a bunch of gems, his head, and 2 random epics for about half an hour of work (going through those trash packs was annoying...). We just vendored everything and came out with about 25ish more gold (5 g per token, + ~10 gold from the 2 random items). \n\n1 protection warrior (me)\n1 holy paladin (T7.5/T8 mix)\n1 fury warrior (T7.5~ish gear)\n\nI tanked 4 of the channelers at 12 o'clock, while the fury warrior took a channeler, one by one, to the 6 o'clock position. the healer stood in the center of the room to reach both of us.\n\nthe fury warrior would grab a channeler one by one as he killed them, so they wouldn't heal each other. it worked just fine. i think we had about 2 standing by the time mag came around. \n\na tip would be to make sure to avoid getting hit by cave ins, as they do about 27k damage if you get hit by one after mag hits 30%.\n\nmag hits like a sissy now...", "date": "2009-06-06T17:18:06-05:00", "rating": 9, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "yea just 3 manned it also. prot warrior, resto druid and mage. it was slow because the mage oomed alot and evocation was often interupted but we didn't even kill the adds, just tanked them all. when an add spawned we grabbed it and added to the collection while we burned the boss, lol. We are all 5k gs(addon) so you dont have to be all icc geared to do this. I will try your way for sure, didn't think about seperating the channelers before dpsing them, haha.", "creationdate": "2010-07-08T06:52:15-05:00", "id": 172077, "rating": 1, "commentid": 739061, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "collector", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2010-04-28T14:19:13-05:00", 1, "Queggy"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 35, "id": 771712, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "310456", "body": "His voice can be heard while doing the instance Blood Furnace. \r\n\"My blood will be the end of you!\"\r\n\"Take my blood and choke on it!\"\r\n\"Illidan is an arrogant fool! I will crush him and reclaim Outland as my own.\"", "date": "2009-07-08T12:09:34-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "yeah, he's [b]bloody[/b] annoying [small]get it? bloody...[/small]", "creationdate": "2010-11-26T09:41:19-06:00", "id": 195311, "rating": 6, "commentid": 771712, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Mageonius", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 36, "id": 790523, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "thantik", "body": "I really wish I would of read this page before I 3 manned him.  Did him with Prot Paladin (me), Resto Druid, and Shadow Priest and we couldn't interrupt the healers so I just tanked it all and kept taunting spawns off the other two.\r\n\r\nIt's actually pretty fun to accomplish, even though it has a full-week cooldown.", "date": "2009-07-27T19:01:49-05:00", "rating": 0, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 37, "id": 792799, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Dazola", "body": "2 Manned\r\n\r\nFeral Druid(Me) and a Holy Paladin. Both of us were in T8/T8.5.\r\n\r\nWe were about 6 Seconds ahead of Enrage Timer. The Paladin had to do around 700dps to be able to have the Raid(Lol) dps to make the Timer. The Adds are the most annoying part about the fight since new Burning Abyssals spawn every minute and the fact that for some reason at around 30% all the adds decided to bug out and drop aggro.", "date": "2009-07-30T04:58:50-05:00", "rating": 6, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
