{"commentv2": 1, "number": 156, "id": 1830361, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Morbius", "body": "Soloed this with a 85 blood DK in unholy spec for the extra healing from death strike glyph which at the time required you to be in unholy presence. That glyph is useless now for boss fights\n\nStay within range of him or keep him dotted because you might lose aggro and cause him to reset. You can also tank him with your back against a wall.\n\nHere's the video:\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=m2UB8bf8sEU", "date": "2013-03-17T18:48:12-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-03-17T18:49:23-05:00", 1, "Morbius"]}
